Neural networks (cs.NE) is another likely sub-category as the paper proposes a new architecture for neural networks. 

Artificial intelligence (cs.AI) is also a possible sub-category as the paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques for improving the performance of neural networks. 

Finally, natural language processing (cs.CL) is a less likely sub-category as the paper does not directly involve language processing, but it does discuss the use of convolutional neural networks for image classification, which can be applied to natural language processing tasks such as text classification.
